# Linux Shell Assignment

# Project Overview
This project contains shell scripts created as part of a Linux command-line assignment.  
The scripts demonstrate basic shell scripting concepts such as file operations, system monitoring, and text writing.


# Shell Scripts

## 1. backup.sh
-Taking a backup snapshot of a directory with timestamp 

## 2. monitor.sh
- Displays running processes or system performance.
- Uses commands like top, ps, or monitoring utilities.

## 3. download.sh
-Downloading a file from the internet
-write it to a predefined directory

# To Run the Scripts

 Give execution permission:
   ```bash
   chmod +x scriptname.sh
